{"id": "art-229", "label": "Art. 229", "title": "Art. 229", "slug": "art-229", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 229 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)Contractul\ncolectiv de munc&#259; este conven&#355;ia încheiat&#259; în form&#259;\nscris&#259; între angajator sau organiza&#355;ia patronal&#259;, de o parte,\n&#351;i salaria&#355;i, reprezenta&#355;i prin sindicate ori în alt mod\nprev&#259;zut de lege, de cealalt&#259; parte, prin care se stabilesc clauze\nprivind condi&#355;iile de munc&#259;, salarizarea, precum &#351;i alte\ndrepturi &#351;i obliga&#355;ii ce decurg din raporturile de munc&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1686754171\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1171\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1686754171\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Negocierea colectiv&#259; la nivel de unitate este\nobligatorie, cu excep&#355;ia cazului în care angajatorul are încadra&#355;i\nmai pu&#355;in de 10 salaria&#355;i.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)La negocierea clauzelor &#351;i\nla încheierea contractelor colective de munc&#259; p&#259;r&#355;ile sunt egale\n&#351;i libere.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1859168094\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1170\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1859168094\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Contractele colective de munc&#259;, încheiate cu\nrespectarea dispozi&#355;iilor legale, constituie legea p&#259;r&#355;ilor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2007126536\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1169\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2007126536\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Contractele colective de munc&#259; la nivel\nna&#355;ional, la nivel de sector de negociere colectiv&#259; &#351;i la nivel\nde grup de unit&#259;&#355;i, precum &#351;i actele adi&#355;ionale la acestea\nsunt publicate pe pagina de internet a Ministerului Muncii &#351;i\nSolidarit&#259;&#355;ii Sociale, în conformitate cu prevederile art. 112 alin.\n(2) din Legea nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>367/2022</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, cu modific&#259;rile &#351;i complet&#259;rile\nulterioare.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}